1
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:49,840
My wrath bristles through my helmet

2
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,520
As I lean against the railing

3
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:56,040
The driving rain has ceased

4
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,920
I raise my eyes

5
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:02,560
And let out a long roar to the sky

6
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,440
My heart surging with passion

7
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:11,080
Thirty years of deeds are but dust and earth

8
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:18,720
A journey of eight thousand li under clouds and moon

9
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,760
Do not idly

10
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:25,720
Let a young man's hair turn white

11
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:33,920
Leaving only empty regret

12
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,000
Lord Director

13
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:47,120
I'll go find some food and drink for the little one

14
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:56,600
Lord Director

15
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,520
It's just a little eunuch

16
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:05,720
There is nothing the Depots cannot find out

17
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:08,480
Only things the Depots do not wish to know

18
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,840
But the robbery was clearly instigated by Wang Zhi

19
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:11,600
You

20
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,920
Why did you not expose him?

21
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:21,000
That you were able to hold back today

22
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,360
Is already progress

23
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,080
This case

24
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,680
Must have a result

25
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,320
As for the process

26
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,760
It is no longer important

27
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,200
Wang Zhi

28
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,800
Will not sacrifice a rook to save a pawn

29
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,040
He is merely using this opportunity

30
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,120
To rattle the Eastern Depot

31
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,280
Let him be

32
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,760
You just focus on working with the Grand Court

33
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:43,840
To investigate the case

34
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,760
Gather evidence on the suspects

35
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:48,600
Finding Li Chenyang is the key

36
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,720
As for the Eastern Depot's affairs

37
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,720
You need not worry

38
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:58,480
I will follow Lord Director's arrangements in everything

39
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:11,160
That devil from the Minister of Personnel's family

40
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:11,920
Recently

41
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,840
Has he caused you any trouble?

42
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:17,040
Yuan Ling has restrained his arrogance quite a bit

43
00:04:18,280 --> 00:04:19,880
But without that overbearing manner

44
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,000
He seems less lively

45
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,680
He knows your identity

46
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,040
Yet still treats you this way

47
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,680
You may associate with him socially

48
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:35,760
But do not trust him with your heart

49
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,280
People only see

50
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,240
His scoundrel-like behavior

51
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,640
But they do not know he

52
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,480
Is smooth in handling matters

53
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:47,320
Minister Yuan has three sons

54
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,280
Yet he favors him alone

55
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,200
Not without reason

56
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,200
The Minister's residence

57
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,600
You should visit more often in the future

58
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,320
Lord Director is right to remind me

59
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,480
All right

60
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,800
I am weary

61
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,760
Staying here does no good for solving the case

62
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:13,880
I must trouble Lord Pei and Lord Zhang

63
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:17,080
To take good care of my son

64
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,560
Lord Director

65
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,400
My, Shang Hua's, godson

66
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,520
Needs no concealment

67
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,480
Nor does he need to demean himself

68
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,560
To be acknowledged

69
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:36,640
Thank you, Lord Director, for protecting the Grand Court

70
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:39,720
Commissioner Shen is young and talented

71
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:42,360
His future is bound to be limitless

72
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:43,760
I

73
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:46,840
Will take them and leave first

74
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,560
Qianben

75
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:07,920
What are your orders, My Lord?

76
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,120
From now on,

77
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:11,520
you are responsible for tracking Shen Youzhi and Zhang Yi.

78
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,560
Keep a close watch on their movements at all times.

79
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,920
Especially that Zhang Yi.

80
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:19,760
I really dislike the way he looks at me.

81
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:22,080
I want the pleasure of eliminating him.

82
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,920
But your safety...

83
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:29,040
I am different from that Shang Hua.

84
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,720
He likes to put on an act and sing opera.

85
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:32,840
As for me,

86
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:35,320
I prefer tangible things.

87
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,160
You brat.

88
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,320
You didn't listen to my arrangements.

89
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:45,400
You confessed without permission.

90
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,200
Minister Pei, you shouldn't have taken the blame.

91
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,800
The historians will record this.

92
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,640
A lifetime of achievements turned into a stain.

93
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,000
To stand up for someone like me

94
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,880
who just muddles along in the Grand Court of Justice,

95
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,720
is not worth it.

96
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:56,400
You...

97
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,800
Minister Pei, please calm down.

98
00:06:58,640 --> 00:06:59,720
Vice Minister Zhang

99
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,520
meant well.

100
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:06,080
If the Lord Director hadn't protected us today,

101
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,960
your head would have been severed long ago.

102
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,920
Hurry up and thank Commissioner Shen.

103
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,080
Many thanks, Lord Shen,

104
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,720
for asking the Lord Director to intervene.

105
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,360
But I also saved your life last night.

106
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:22,560
So we're even.

107
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,080
I am old.

108
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,320
I view you as my own child.

109
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,280
I cannot bear

110
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:31,040
the pain of the white-haired burying the black-haired.

111
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,400
Nowadays, fame and fortune to me

112
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,880
are nothing but fleeting clouds.

113
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,800
The position of Minister of the Grand Court of Justice

114
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,720
in exchange for two lives

115
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,640
and keeping the Grand Court of Justice stable...

116
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,160
is not a loss.

117
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,480
Next time,

118
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,440
do not be so impulsive again.

119
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,840
All right, Minister Pei.

120
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,800
A dignified official of the third rank

121
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,600
sighing at the gates of the Eastern Depot...

122
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,480
If people see this,

123
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,600
there will be gossip again.

124
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:56,040
Lord Director Wang's martial arts are very vicious.

125
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,880
We survived a great disaster today.

126
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,160
We must hurry to investigate the case in the next two days.

127
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:03,200
Do not slack off.

128
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,000
Understood.

129
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,960
That Lord Director Wang could become head of the Western Depot

130
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,560
and win battles from a thousand miles away

131
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,960
naturally means he has extraordinary abilities.

132
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:11,640
By the way,

133
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:12,640
regarding this point,

134
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,000
Lord Shen knows better than us.

135
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:17,560
I don't know.

136
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:20,160
I only care about doing my duty.

137
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,200
Then let's go.

138
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,760
Let's go do our duty.

139
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:28,920
So,

140
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,520
your duty

141
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:31,920
is just eating snacks?

142
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,320
This isn't out of selfishness.

143
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:35,480
Tell me,

144
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,520
isn't this location excellent?

145
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,080
What is this thing? This...

146
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,320
This is from Zheng He's voyages to the Western Seas,

147
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,600
an item he brought back.

148
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,480
Usually,

149
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:16,640
one eats wild plums and grapes in June.

150
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:21,760
You say I can eat these plums and grapes in April.

151
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,960
Does that count as a skill?

152
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,240
Enough, stop pretending.

153
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:32,000
Since you are already awake,

154
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,680
why not open your eyes quickly?

155
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:36,720
Let me get a good look at your heaven-and-earth-shaking skills.

156
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,960
Lady Hua, stop it.

157
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:43,480
What happened last night must have spread among my colleagues.

158
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,120
My face of over thirty years,

159
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,800
is completely lost.

160
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,880
So you're saying,

161
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,520
you regret entering my Blossom Pavilion?

162
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,960
Regret?

163
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,560
I regret knowing you.

164
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,280
The beauty is like the moon,

165
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,560
seen once, never forgotten.

166
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:09,480
Gazing at the moon, I think of her,

167
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,400
thinking of her drives me mad.

168
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,760
My Lord serves in the Ministry of Rites in the palace,

169
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:20,680
surely you know who sent this?

170
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:29,560
Even if Lord Director Wang has a heart that longs for a beauty,

171
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,480
there are things he cannot give you.

172
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,520
Why not,

173
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:45,080
you give your most valuable possession to Lord Director Wang,

174
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,920
in exchange for me?

175
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:50,480
This...

176
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,040
Are you afraid, My Lord?

177
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,440
On one side is the Eastern Depot,

178
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,360
on the other is the Western Depot.

179
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,080
Is it difficult?

180
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:04,720
Or do you feel,

181
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:09,720
I am not worth you redeeming me?

182
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:21,080
I'll trade! It's worth it even if I die.

183
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:37,920
Please forgive me, Lord Director.

184
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,280
This thing is shy.

185
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:48,880
Animals fear the look in people's eyes,

186
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:51,000
which cannot be disguised.

187
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,480
It doesn't matter.

188
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,280
I have always been,

189
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:57,120
unloved by these things.

190
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:05,080
Perhaps when I was young,

191
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,680
my aura was too hostile.

192
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:08,840
Lord Director,

193
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:09,920
you overthink it.

194
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,520
You are naturally,

195
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,280
a person of endless good fortune.

196
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:21,280
I do believe in the word "fortune".

197
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:23,120
Right now,

198
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:25,320
I should be in my hometown, Fengling Town,

199
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:28,160
tending to a small plot of land,

200
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,560
gossiping about domestic trifles,

201
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:31,080
spending my days with a house full of children and grandchildren.

202
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:37,800
Let's not talk about these useless things.

203
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,000
Regarding Consort Wan,

204
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,120
how is she lately?

205
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:45,600
Consort Wan,

206
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:47,880
ever since the one-year-old little prince died young,

207
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,960
has had no destiny with royal heirs.

208
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,840
So she places her affection on these little things,

209
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,320
cherishing them dearly.

210
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:58,120
Her favor remains undiminished,

211
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,360
yet she has no fate for children.

212
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:03,920
And she isn't willing to pave the way for others.

213
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,520
This Consort Wan of ours,

214
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:08,000
is both formidable,

215
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:10,040
and foolish.

216
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:19,880
Why aren't you speaking?

217
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:23,440
I was teasing the cat just now.

218
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:24,720
I didn't hear anything.

219
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,680
Lord Director...

220
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:33,400
Speak.

221
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,640
News just came from the palace.

222
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:38,120
Today,

223
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:39,560
Wang Zhi returned to the palace in a hurry.

224
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,400
It is because...

225
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,720
Did I raise a

226
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:45,960
cowardly piece of trash?

227
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:48,520
The little prince was taken into the palace by Consort Wan.

228
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:49,560
You may leave for now.

229
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:50,000
Lord Director...

230
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:50,840
Leave.

231
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:52,840
Yes.

232
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:22,760
As for me,

233
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:25,560
I've never cared much for such things.

234
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,480
Things that sap one's will.

235
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:30,440
Some treat it like a child,

236
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:31,920
but I...

237
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:34,600
I merely see it as a source of amusement.

238
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,800
But one day,

239
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:40,840
I saw my godson, Youzhi,

240
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,560
with a little beast,

241
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:45,240
showing a smile full of vulnerability.

242
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,560
I suddenly realized

243
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:49,600
he wasn't ruthless enough.

244
00:14:50,160 --> 00:14:51,240
He still had weaknesses.

245
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,680
So, the very next day,

246
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,160
that little beast

247
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:57,400
lay dead at his door.

248
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:02,560
From then on,

249
00:15:03,680 --> 00:15:05,480
he has never been distracted

250
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:06,680
by anything else.

251
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,200
Lord Director,

252
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,000
this lowly one will go fetch the cat.

253
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,760
Truly intelligent.

254
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,520
Just a bit too clever.

255
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:35,240
What young eunuch, upon seeing me,

256
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:38,000
only pretends to be afraid,

257
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:40,600
but has no fear in his eyes?

258
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:55,440
Light on his feet,

259
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,680
leaving no trace.

260
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:01,440
Run along.

261
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:02,920
Once you run,

262
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:06,120
don't ever come back.

263
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:27,680
That old fox.

264
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:29,920
He must have noticed something off about me.

265
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:44,960
The hour of demons.

266
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:47,000
Yin and Yang interchange.

267
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:49,240
No taboos apply.

268
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:51,040
All evil retreat.

269
00:16:51,920 --> 00:16:53,320
It is the You hour.

270
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,120
Light the lamps.

271
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:59,080
Any news on Li Chenyang from the Embroidered Uniform Guard?

272
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,680
The Guards who chased out of the city yesterday

273
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,800
have all reported back by carrier pigeon.

274
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:04,920
Among those who left the city last night,

275
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:06,840
Li Chenyang was not seen.

276
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:08,080
The trail has gone cold.

277
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:11,600
We can only start from here.

278
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:14,080
This must be our focus.

279
00:17:15,600 --> 00:17:17,200
Tang Xi and the Western Depot conspired

280
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,440
to abduct Li Chenyang.

281
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,520
If it were just to strike at the Eastern Depot, fine.

282
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:23,000
But I fear

283
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:25,840
they will harm my Godfather.

284
00:17:26,360 --> 00:17:27,440
Still worrying about your Godfather?

285
00:17:33,600 --> 00:17:34,920
Vice Minister Zhang loves sweets.

286
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:39,560
When I'm feeling down,

287
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:41,240
I like to eat something sweet.

288
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,200
Having a bit of sugar

289
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:42,960
makes me feel better.

290
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,680
It gradually became a habit.

291
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:47,120
For someone as lazy and unambitious as you,

292
00:17:47,760 --> 00:17:49,240
what troubles could you possibly have?

293
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,400
It's just an excuse for your gluttony.

294
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:52,800
Since you like them,

295
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:53,880
next time I'll bring you

296
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,000
something different from the Palace to try.

297
00:17:55,760 --> 00:17:56,840
That is very thoughtful of you, Lord Shen.

298
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:58,640
But the two of us certainly can't compare.

299
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:00,880
Lord Shen comes from a prestigious background.

300
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:02,800
The godson of Lord Director Shang.

301
00:18:03,760 --> 00:18:04,440
Although you are an adopted son,

302
00:18:05,040 --> 00:18:06,080
Lord Director Shang has placed

303
00:18:06,080 --> 00:18:07,320
deep and high hopes on you.

304
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:08,400
Look at you, so young,

305
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:09,840
yet already holding the rank of Commissioner.

306
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,920
You can't slack off for even a moment.

307
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:13,800
In one's position,

308
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:14,880
one must fulfill one's duties.

309
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:16,320
In my view,

310
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:17,200
slacking off

311
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:19,360
is dereliction of duty.

312
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,560
Only by being strict with oneself

313
00:18:22,120 --> 00:18:23,800
can one be a model for subordinates.

314
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:24,760
Even if

315
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:27,240
others know I am the Eastern Depot Director's godson,

316
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:28,400
neither I nor my Godfather

317
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,720
will be accused of abusing power for personal gain.

318
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:32,400
To stand firm in the court,

319
00:18:32,560 --> 00:18:34,040
I must be unyielding in my duty

320
00:18:34,360 --> 00:18:35,600
and earn true respect.

321
00:18:36,080 --> 00:18:38,320
Truly a noble family with great ambitions.

322
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:39,760
How could people like you understand

323
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:42,040
the joys of us humble folk?

324
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,360
If one day you feel suffocated,

325
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:45,240
just tell me.

326
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:47,080
I'll take you to experience

327
00:18:47,280 --> 00:18:48,640
the joys of a lazy man in the capital.

328
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,880
Consider it repayment for the sweets you bring me.

329
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,160
Deal.

330
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:02,840
My Lord

331
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,440
You look radiant with joy

332
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,720
Is there a happy occasion?

333
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,360
The three great joys of life

334
00:19:07,800 --> 00:19:09,120
I have claimed them all today

335
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:11,960
My life is truly complete

336
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:14,760
Congratulations, My Lord

337
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:40,400
The breathing is short and steady

338
00:19:40,600 --> 00:19:42,040
Such a strong murderous aura

339
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,520
It is the smell of blood

340
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:52,880
Regarding the little prince

341
00:19:53,600 --> 00:19:54,800
If you do not go to inquire

342
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:57,360
I have my own ways of finding out

343
00:19:58,840 --> 00:20:00,520
I am but a woman of the pleasure quarters

344
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,680
Sleeping with one more

345
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:04,400
Or one less

346
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,360
What difference does it make?

347
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:08,840
Besides

348
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:13,560
You are different from them

349
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:15,280
How am I different?

350
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:18,680
Before, you sent secret reports to the Eastern Depot

351
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:21,560
Now you have switched to the Western Depot

352
00:20:22,840 --> 00:20:24,040
In the end, I cannot escape

353
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:25,480
The grasp of you and Shang Hua

354
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:28,240
If you do not wish to stay in Blossom Pavilion

355
00:20:28,800 --> 00:20:30,880
You can live at my estate in the suburbs

356
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:32,320
And be the mistress of the house

357
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:35,040
You are free

358
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:56,320
This is the pastry

359
00:20:56,840 --> 00:20:58,640
His Majesty bestowed upon Consort Wan

360
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:00,160
You should taste it too

361
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:01,800
Your mood

362
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:04,080
Might improve a little

363
00:21:06,080 --> 00:21:08,040
Consort Wan is truly fortunate

364
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:10,800
If I said

365
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:12,600
I wanted to be Consort Wan

366
00:21:13,360 --> 00:21:14,240
What would you do?

367
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:18,200
Everything Consort Wan has

368
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:20,240
Is bestowed by His Majesty

369
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,240
If you wish to be a consort

370
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:26,800
You might as well bear a little prince

371
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:29,520
And make him the Emperor

372
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:35,520
Lord Shen, Lord Zhang

373
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:37,040
Why are you here?

374
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:39,400
Isn't this Battalion Commander Yuan?

375
00:21:39,720 --> 00:21:41,760
Isn't this the biggest obstacle to Lord Shen

376
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:43,680
Asserting authority before the Embroidered Uniform Guard?

377
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:46,640
I would not call him an obstacle

378
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,760
Battalion Commander Yuan's heart is not in the court

379
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:49,800
His heart

380
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:51,400
Is with the lonely smoke of the desert

381
00:21:51,840 --> 00:21:52,880
And fighting on the battlefield

382
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,680
Where do you think Battalion Commander Yuan's courtesy

383
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:56,680
Towards you comes from?

384
00:21:57,120 --> 00:21:58,720
It is good that Lord Shen knows

385
00:21:59,520 --> 00:22:01,160
Three years ago, I ran away from home

386
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:02,520
To join the Divine Machine Battalion

387
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:06,520
But General Lin received a letter from my father

388
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:08,320
And refused to take me

389
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,280
Give it a rest

390
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:10,880
With that little skill of yours

391
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:12,640
Is not even enough for your father to collect your corpse

392
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:13,760
You have the nerve to say that

393
00:22:18,120 --> 00:22:19,160
What exactly are you doing?

394
00:22:19,560 --> 00:22:21,640
Monitoring the movements of Tang Xi and the others

395
00:22:22,320 --> 00:22:23,040
Tang Xi?

396
00:22:24,560 --> 00:22:25,760
How could she be in this courtyard?

397
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,520
I just saw her go out

398
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:29,240
Let me see

399
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:29,720
What?

400
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:31,760
You saw her go out?

401
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:34,960
Young hero

402
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:37,040
Young hero

403
00:22:38,760 --> 00:22:40,040
I was rude earlier

404
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,320
Give me a straight answer

405
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,840
Can I resign from the Embroidered Uniform Guard

406
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:44,480
And join your Four Directions Organization?

407
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,520
Battalion Commander Yuan

408
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:48,720
Do you want to ruin your father

409
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:49,840
Or ruin us?

410
00:22:50,320 --> 00:22:51,800
I told you to call me Yuan Ling

411
00:22:52,080 --> 00:22:52,720
Don't go

412
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:53,240
Where are you going?

413
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:53,840
I have matters to attend to

414
00:22:59,360 --> 00:22:59,760
Oh no

415
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:00,960
It is a dummy

416
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,200
Tang Xi really did go out

417
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:02,760
Yuan Ling

418
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:04,600
Why didn't you report Tang Xi's movements?

419
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:06,400
Do I need to report friendly sparring to you?

420
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:07,760
What rotten luck

421
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:09,080
You brainless, stubborn rascal

422
00:23:17,880 --> 00:23:18,400
My lord

423
00:23:18,600 --> 00:23:19,280
Care to join me?

424
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:20,840
My newly developed foot bath soak

425
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:24,720
Where is Tang Xi?

426
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,400
Who said this is Tang Xi?

427
00:23:27,120 --> 00:23:27,800
My lords,

428
00:23:28,320 --> 00:23:29,720
you have too much internal heat.

429
00:23:30,320 --> 00:23:30,960
Are you sure

430
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:33,240
you don't want to join me for a healthy foot bath?

431
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:36,600
Who are you lords visiting?

432
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:38,440
Or are you, without permission,

433
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,520
trespassing on a private residence?

434
00:23:40,560 --> 00:23:41,840
We are not trespassing.

435
00:23:42,160 --> 00:23:42,760
It was Wu Qiangu

436
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:44,160
who invited us to soak our feet together.

437
00:23:44,800 --> 00:23:46,160
No wonder it smells so bad.

438
00:23:47,640 --> 00:23:49,000
Where has Young Master Tang Xi gone?

439
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:50,480
Haven't seen you for half a day,

440
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,320
and Lord Zhang misses me already?

441
00:23:55,320 --> 00:23:56,560
That's a bit much.

442
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:58,640
Young Master Tang reads too many storybooks.

443
00:23:59,080 --> 00:24:00,280
Spouting nonsense as soon as he speaks.

444
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,520
Young Master Tang,

445
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:03,480
where did you go today?

446
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:05,200
Just wandered around a bit.

447
00:24:06,320 --> 00:24:07,480
We even met, didn't we?

448
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,560
Forgot?

449
00:24:09,280 --> 00:24:12,040
The peach blossom tree in Commissioner Shen's courtyard

450
00:24:13,360 --> 00:24:15,240
is blooming exceptionally beautifully.

451
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:22,560
Lord Shen,

452
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:25,000
remember to tell Lord Shen

453
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:27,120
I left something behind for him to take care of.

454
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:29,520
Young hero,

455
00:24:30,320 --> 00:24:31,840
I learned that move you taught me.

456
00:24:32,360 --> 00:24:32,880
Battalion Commander Yuan,

457
00:24:33,760 --> 00:24:34,920
when did you get so close to her?

458
00:24:36,320 --> 00:24:37,720
Lord Zhang, are you jealous?

459
00:24:38,600 --> 00:24:39,520
Mind your status.

460
00:24:40,600 --> 00:24:41,040
Time to eat.

461
00:24:41,040 --> 00:24:41,680
Lord Zhang,

462
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:42,640
let's eat first,

463
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:43,520
then worry about status.

464
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:45,040
I think we can try a different approach.

465
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:46,160
Infiltrate the Four Directions Organization,

466
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:47,280
and make friends first.

467
00:24:49,320 --> 00:24:50,840
We only prepared enough for four.

468
00:24:51,080 --> 00:24:52,000
Not a single portion more.

469
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:55,320
Safe travels, I won't see you out.

470
00:25:05,280 --> 00:25:06,240
The secret reports within the Eastern Depot

471
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,560
are just official documents for show.

472
00:25:08,120 --> 00:25:09,560
And the crimes they fabricated,

473
00:25:09,560 --> 00:25:10,960
framing loyalists and torturing for confessions,

474
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:11,480
are not recorded there.

475
00:25:11,840 --> 00:25:13,640
But the secret archive acts as a bridge

476
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:15,120
between the Depot and the intelligence.

477
00:25:15,360 --> 00:25:15,960
If the bridge is broken,

478
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:16,640
then the path is blocked.

479
00:25:16,960 --> 00:25:18,480
Therefore, a secret archive must exist.

480
00:25:20,080 --> 00:25:21,320
But based on my observation of Shang Hua today,

481
00:25:21,320 --> 00:25:22,440
and knowing his daily routine,

482
00:25:22,560 --> 00:25:23,400
inside the Eastern Depot,

483
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:25,600
there is no secret entrance or underground palace.

484
00:25:26,280 --> 00:25:27,320
Did you check the locations I gave you?

485
00:25:28,080 --> 00:25:28,600
Thoroughly.

486
00:25:28,840 --> 00:25:29,920
If it's not inside the Eastern Depot,

487
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:30,760
what about outside?

488
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,520
Shang Hua's health is much worse than before.

489
00:25:32,560 --> 00:25:33,400
He rarely goes out.

490
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:34,600
But there is one place

491
00:25:34,600 --> 00:25:35,560
he visits once every month.

492
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:37,640
Brilliant.

493
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:39,560
Our Great Ming holds Buddhism in high regard.

494
00:25:40,120 --> 00:25:40,880
If the Eastern Depot

495
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:41,840
places the secret archive

496
00:25:41,840 --> 00:25:43,760
in a place ordinary people dare not touch,

497
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:45,160
or even a place they revere,

498
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,320
that would be the safest.

499
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:47,400
Exactly.

500
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:50,160
And the place Shang Hua visits every month

501
00:25:52,440 --> 00:25:53,360
is Linggu Temple.

502
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:56,320
If we just pretend to offer incense at Linggu Temple

503
00:25:56,320 --> 00:25:57,280
and sneak in wearing plain clothes,

504
00:25:57,520 --> 00:25:59,080
that would be easy for us.

505
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:00,400
But we need to reach

506
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:01,840
the core area of Linggu Temple to investigate.

507
00:26:02,040 --> 00:26:03,000
That won't be so easy.

508
00:26:03,560 --> 00:26:04,640
Striking the enemy's heart,

509
00:26:04,760 --> 00:26:06,640
driving straight in is the most satisfying way.

510
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:07,480
Do not be careless.

511
00:26:07,720 --> 00:26:09,960
The core tower of Linggu Temple is built on a peak,

512
00:26:10,120 --> 00:26:11,920
amidst dense bamboo and deep valleys.

513
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:13,720
The Eastern Depot ordered Master Konghui

514
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:15,600
to set up the Celestial Mechanism Array using the terrain

515
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:17,040
to block any intruders.

516
00:26:17,320 --> 00:26:19,880
The sixty-four hexagrams change infinitely,

517
00:26:20,280 --> 00:26:21,640
shifting eight ways in different directions,

518
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:23,120
attacking with different methods.

519
00:26:23,360 --> 00:26:24,760
Combined with Qimen Dunjia,

520
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:27,200
it conceals the Linggu Temple tower within.

521
00:26:27,360 --> 00:26:28,120
Tomorrow at Sishi,

522
00:26:28,280 --> 00:26:29,200
we will enter Linggu Temple,

523
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,520
find the Twelve Gates of Life,

524
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,600
break the array, and enter the tower.

525
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:33,720
Here.

526
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,280
Did that darn Little Xi

527
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:39,840
leave you behind?

528
00:26:51,840 --> 00:26:52,600
Youzhi.

529
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:53,640
Why are you here?

530
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:55,280
I was worried about your health, Godfather,

531
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:57,040
so I came back to visit.

532
00:27:10,520 --> 00:27:10,960
Godfather,

533
00:27:11,080 --> 00:27:11,640
your hand...

534
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:15,120
It's nothing.

535
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:21,320
A little jerk refused to be disciplined.

536
00:27:21,560 --> 00:27:22,640
Once Consort Wan

537
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,200
takes a liking to a new toy,

538
00:27:25,760 --> 00:27:26,720
this jerk's life

539
00:27:27,120 --> 00:27:28,320
will come to an end.

540
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:35,520
Jifeng greets Lord Shang Hua.

541
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:37,520
That two-faced dog

542
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:38,480
has been taken care of for you.

543
00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:40,640
Please inspect.

544
00:27:42,520 --> 00:27:43,560
Such a filthy thing,

545
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:45,520
Mr. Jifeng, dispose of it as you please.

546
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:47,000
Why bring it back to dirty the courtyard?

547
00:27:47,280 --> 00:27:48,480
I told him to bring it.

548
00:27:49,840 --> 00:27:52,080
Only this can relieve my pent-up anger.

549
00:27:54,160 --> 00:27:55,160
He sent a painting

550
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:56,920
of the river where I fell from grace

551
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:58,200
just to upset me, and I let it pass.

552
00:27:58,840 --> 00:27:59,880
But today he even extended his hand

553
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,560
to the one I've planned around for years,

554
00:28:01,560 --> 00:28:02,680
the Little Prince.

555
00:28:04,200 --> 00:28:05,400
This Wang Zhi

556
00:28:06,040 --> 00:28:07,360
is becoming increasingly unruly.

557
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:09,840
Youzhi, Jifeng.

558
00:28:10,320 --> 00:28:11,200
Go back and prepare.

559
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:12,480
Tomorrow,

560
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:14,160
accompany me to Linggu Temple.

561
00:28:15,560 --> 00:28:16,720
It is time to see

562
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:17,920
how Mingyu is progressing

563
00:28:18,080 --> 00:28:19,440
with the collection of secret reports.

564
00:28:19,760 --> 00:28:20,200
Yes.

565
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:23,200
Then I

566
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,240
will not disturb your rest any longer, Godfather.

567
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:49,840
My Lord.

568
00:28:50,600 --> 00:28:52,000
Shen Youzhi is Shang Hua's godson.

569
00:28:52,440 --> 00:28:53,720
When did you find out, My Lord?

570
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:55,960
Two years ago, when Shen Youzhi

571
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:57,520
took charge of the Embroidered Uniform Guard,

572
00:28:57,520 --> 00:28:58,720
there were already rumors.

573
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:01,000
I tell you to study the official registry,

574
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:02,480
but you just won't listen.

575
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,080
Everyone knows

576
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:05,280
Wang Zhi

577
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:07,080
climbed up via Consort Wan,

578
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:09,200
stepping on Shang Hua's head

579
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,640
to become Lord Director of the Western Depot.

580
00:29:12,080 --> 00:29:13,000
So how could Shang Hua

581
00:29:13,120 --> 00:29:14,920
not groom another godson

582
00:29:15,120 --> 00:29:16,680
to take over the Eastern Depot's power?

583
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:19,680
What Shang Hua said today...

584
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:21,920
Do you think he's trying to win us over?

585
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:24,240
He used the Minister of Personnel as a pretext

586
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:25,200
to warn us.

587
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:27,520
The struggle between the Eastern and Western Depots

588
00:29:27,520 --> 00:29:29,320
hasn't just been going on for a day or two.

589
00:29:32,160 --> 00:29:33,720
If even the Minister of Personnel

590
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:36,080
is showing favor to the Eastern Depot,

591
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,800
then for our Grand Court's next investigation,

592
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:40,720
we must choose the right side

593
00:29:41,080 --> 00:29:42,840
to avoid disaster.

594
00:29:44,280 --> 00:29:45,320
It's really too complicated.

595
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:48,080
It'd be less worry to just go home and farm.

596
00:29:49,080 --> 00:29:50,960
I had a chance to go home and farm today,

597
00:29:51,440 --> 00:29:52,720
but you ruined it completely.

598
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:55,960
My Lord.

599
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:56,880
I'll go take a look.

600
00:30:01,720 --> 00:30:02,440
Who is it?

601
00:30:02,760 --> 00:30:03,840
Banging on the door this late at night.

602
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:06,360
It's Lord Shen.

603
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:09,920
Lord Shen, visiting so late...

604
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:10,840
what is the matter?

605
00:30:12,080 --> 00:30:13,360
I am going to Linggu Temple tomorrow.

606
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,560
I have no time to look after it.

607
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,000
The debt Little Xi owes...

608
00:30:17,280 --> 00:30:17,760
you pay it.

609
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:22,520
Take good care of it.

610
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:29,080
Tomorrow, Shang Hua

611
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,720
will definitely go to Linggu Temple

612
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:32,440
to seek a divination from Master Konghui.

613
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:33,840
Linggu Temple...

614
00:30:35,120 --> 00:30:36,280
Ever since Shang Hua

615
00:30:36,600 --> 00:30:38,120
took us to see Master Konghui

616
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,400
for a fortune reading,

617
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:42,120
I haven't been back there.

618
00:30:43,320 --> 00:30:44,480
Master Konghui

619
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:46,520
is revered by both the court and the commoners.

620
00:30:46,840 --> 00:30:47,440
He also possesses the ability

621
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:49,440
to divine and foresee destiny.

622
00:30:50,120 --> 00:30:51,440
If you want to get a reading,

623
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:53,680
let's go together tomorrow.

624
00:30:53,840 --> 00:30:54,800
Let's go join the fun.

625
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:56,760
Are you going or not?

626
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,440
Let's talk when I wake up tomorrow.

627
00:31:27,040 --> 00:31:28,200
Tang Xi, Young Master of the Tang Clan,

628
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:30,080
has come to pay respects to Master Konghui.

629
00:31:30,520 --> 00:31:33,280
Going down the mountain is easy; going up is hard.

630
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,320
Young Master Tang,

631
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:36,280
you should not have returned.

632
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,200
Qimen Dunjia guards the Spirit Pagoda.

633
00:31:43,080 --> 00:31:44,920
Eight formations transform into sixty-four.

634
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:46,200
Master Konghui,

635
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:48,720
do you know of the Celestial Mechanism Array?

636
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:51,840
The living are merely passersby;

637
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:54,240
the dead are the ones returning home.

638
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:57,960
Once you enter the Celestial Mechanism Array,

639
00:31:58,400 --> 00:32:01,440
it becomes a matter of life and death.

640
00:32:04,520 --> 00:32:05,520
Today, the area around Linggu Temple

641
00:32:05,520 --> 00:32:07,680
is strictly guarded by the Grand Court of Justice
and the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

642
00:32:08,280 --> 00:32:10,240
Forcing your way in will be fraught with difficulties.

643
00:32:10,320 --> 00:32:12,400
The Celestial Mechanism Array, on the first of the month,
from the Hour of the Snake to the Horse...

644
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,280
is the optimal time.

645
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:14,480
Today,

646
00:32:15,040 --> 00:32:16,960
we have only this one chance to break the formation.

647
00:32:17,760 --> 00:32:19,160
What if I insist on entering the game?

648
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:25,280
Young Master Tang,

649
00:32:25,600 --> 00:32:28,520
do you have the heart to kill Buddha?

650
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:29,800
Naturally,

651
00:32:30,800 --> 00:32:32,000
if Buddha blocks my way, I kill Buddha.

652
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:35,480
Where there is no door, I will force a path.

653
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:39,880
Fate and destiny

654
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:43,560
are chosen by oneself.

655
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:47,720
No door,

656
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,520
force a path.

657
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:50,480
Good.

658
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,960
Worthy of being my disciple.

659
00:33:00,120 --> 00:33:00,560
Shuimo.

660
00:33:00,840 --> 00:33:01,280
Here.

661
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:02,760
How are the arrangements coming along?

662
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,280
Please rest assured, My Lord.

663
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:05,680
To avoid attracting attention,

664
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:07,040
I have had the people from the Grand Court of Justice

665
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:08,760
all disguise themselves as ordinary pilgrims

666
00:33:09,120 --> 00:33:10,280
and infiltrate Linggu Temple.

667
00:33:16,240 --> 00:33:17,320
Zhang Yi, Vice Minister of the Grand Court of Justice,

668
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:18,560
pays respects to the Lord Director.

669
00:33:19,760 --> 00:33:20,680
No need for formalities.

670
00:33:21,800 --> 00:33:23,440
Vice Minister Zhang coming to Linggu Temple...

671
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:25,760
is it because you've hit a dead end in the case,

672
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:28,440
and came to pray to Buddha for the truth?

673
00:33:29,640 --> 00:33:30,960
You jest, Lord Director.

674
00:33:31,280 --> 00:33:32,040
Could it be...

675
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:32,960
Exactly.

676
00:33:34,920 --> 00:33:35,960
Early this morning,

677
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:38,200
Tang Xi, Yuan Ran, and Wu Qiangu

678
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:39,160
disappeared without a trace.

679
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:42,280
The Grand Court of Justice is in charge of monitoring
the Four Directions Organization.

680
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:43,680
How could they suddenly disappear?

681
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:46,880
With the skills of those three,

682
00:33:47,840 --> 00:33:49,080
for the Grand Court officials to lose them

683
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:50,200
is only natural.

684
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:52,160
But fortunately, Lu Shijie's whereabouts

685
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,280
are still under control.

686
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:54,800
Early this morning,

687
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:56,400
he went to Blossom Pavilion very early

688
00:33:56,800 --> 00:33:58,080
to be with the Director of the Western Depot.

689
00:33:59,040 --> 00:33:59,600
At this moment,

690
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:02,240
they should be on their way to Linggu Temple.

691
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:05,240
Therefore, I led my men here to observe,

692
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:06,800
to prevent any accidents.

693
00:34:08,320 --> 00:34:09,720
They linger like ghosts.

694
00:34:11,080 --> 00:34:11,520
Godfather.

695
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:12,680
Then shall we...

696
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:15,960
No need to worry.

697
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:18,920
Master Konghui

698
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,320
communicates with the divine,

699
00:34:20,640 --> 00:34:21,960
transcends the worldly,

700
00:34:22,200 --> 00:34:24,680
has served the state, and is revered by thousands.

701
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:26,440
Their coming to Linggu Temple

702
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:29,920
is merely a bit of posturing,

703
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:32,800
they won't dare to act rashly.

704
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:41,720
Abbot Konghui has been expecting the Lord Director for some time.

705
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:42,880
Please follow me.

706
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:53,520
Benefactor, please stay back.

707
00:34:54,040 --> 00:34:55,560
Abbot Konghui has been unwell recently.

708
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,160
He should not be disturbed in his cultivation.

709
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:58,240
Please forgive us.

710
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,080
Youzhi,

711
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:04,120
wait outside the door.

712
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:05,680
In four hours,

713
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:07,000
come and pick me up.

714
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:08,920
Yes.

715
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:20,640
I wonder what troubles the Lord Director,

716
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:23,160
that he needs Master Konghui to resolve his doubts.

717
00:35:23,720 --> 00:35:25,120
Godfather and Master Konghui

718
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:26,760
have a friendship of gentlemen.

719
00:35:27,080 --> 00:35:27,920
They have known each other for a long time.

720
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:29,760
In his spare time,

721
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:30,960
he often comes to visit.

722
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,360
Is there anything inappropriate about that?

723
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:36,400
No.

724
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:37,480
As long as you are pleased.
